title: DaytonaState InMotion News
projectDescription: During my time at Daytona State College, I assisted the college newspaper with their website as resident Webmaster for about 2 years. This site was originally created using the WordPress CMS. During this time I regularly attended meetings regarding the website, communicated and collaborated with staff writers on articles, managed user accounts, and maintained the legacy systems put in place by previous Webmasters.
